{"id": 7846, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2020", "session": "20N", "subtopic": "3-2-periodic-trends", "title": "20N.1.SL.TZ0.8", "topic_id": "3", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Which oxide will dissolve in water to give the solution with the lowest pH?</span></p>\n<p>A.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi><mn>10</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>B.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>SiO</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>C.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>Al</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math></p>\n<p>D.  <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>MgO</mi></math></p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>Fairly well answered. Almost 70% of candidates could identify that non-metallic oxides would dissolve in water to yield a substance of low pH.</p>\n</div>"}